album.strDescriptionEN: Unlocked is the sophomore studio album by Romanian singer-songwriter and model Alexandra Stan. A special standard edition of the album for Japan was released on August 27, 2014 through Victor and Fonogram Records. The album spawn the five singles "Thanks For Leaving", "Cherry Pop", "Dance", "Give Me Your Everything" and "Vanilla Chocolat" featuring Romanian singer Connect-R. The album has an overall progressive house vibe, with it containing dance-pop, synthpop, reggae fusion and europop as well.
